packages DESCRIPTION files

Source: R/description.R
pacs_description.Rd

packages DESCRIPTION files taken locally or if remotely then from GITHUB CRAN mirror or CRAN website.

pacs_description(
  pacs,
  versions = NULL,
  at = NULL,
  local = FALSE,
  lib.loc = NULL
)

Arguments

pacs

character vector packages names.
versions

character vector versions. Default: NULL
at

Date . Default: NULL
local

logical if to use local library. Default: FALSE
lib.loc

character used optionally when local is equal TRUE. Default: NULL

Value

list of list with names proper for DESCRIPTION file fields.

Examples

pacs_description(c("dplyr", "memoise"), version = c("0.8.1", "1.0.0"))
